title: Can't Lose the Love Handles? Just Do THIS!!
tags: love handles|get rid of love handles|how to get rid of love handles|lose love handles|how to lose love handles|how to lose love handles fast|love handle workout|love handle exercises|exercises for love handles|best exercises for love handles|how to lose fat around waist|lose fat around waistline|lower belly fat|lose lower belly fat|lose lower belly fat fast|athleanx|athlean x|jeff cavaliere|burn fat|lose back fat|oblique exercises|oblique workout
description: If you can‚Äôt lose the love handles no matter how hard you‚Äôve tried, then do exactly what is shown in this video and it will happen faster than you think. The key to getting rid of fat around the waist is to realize that it too, just like all body fat, is something that can be done with persistence and a few important strategies. While there is no such thing as love handle exercises or exercises to burn lower belly fat, there are things you can do in and out of the gym to see results much faster.The first thing you have to do to get rid of fat around the waist or love handles is take a close look at how you‚Äôre eating. Nutrition is and always will be the number one priority when it comes to getting ripped and losing body fat. All too often, people want to skip this part of the equation because it is the one that is most difficult to stay consistent with, but it‚Äôs where all the difference matters.Many people will turn to different kinds of diets in order to lose fat fast. The problem with most diets is that they are temporary solutions to a long term problem. And even when you follow the ‚Äúrules‚Äù of the diet plan, that doesn‚Äôt necessarily mean that you are going to lose fat. For instance, if your keto plan has you avoiding carbs but you still wind up overeating significantly on fats and proteins and are unable to get to a hypo caloric state, you are not going to lose your love handles.Similarly, if you are following a diet strategy like intermittent fasting as a way of losing the fat around the waistline, be advised that simply eating within the proper window does not guarantee success. Again, if you consume more calories than you are burning off you are not going to burn enough fat to get rid of that around your belly.The second big nutrition mistake relates to the first and that is, even if you can do everything right with your nutrition but you quit too soon you likely will not see the results you‚Äôre looking for. Keep in mind that in men especially, waistline and lower belly fat is the last to go. This pertains to the low back as well. You will first start to see fat loss in the face and neck but only when you‚Äôve been consistent for a long period of time will you see the love handles start to disappear. Don‚Äôt give up too soon just because you don‚Äôt see the fat loss in the love handles. Realize that it‚Äôs coming, it just will take a bit more time.As far as training goes, there are some things you can do to get rid of love handles faster. You need to be sure that as the fat loss occurs that the muscles underneath are developed and looking good which will give the appearance of a better looking waistline sooner. Here is where you want to be sure you‚Äôre not just doing traditional ab exercises.Train your obliques. People often say that doing oblique exercises will thicken your waistline. This isn‚Äôt the significant cause of why you have a thick waist, it‚Äôs the body fat laying over the top. So that said, be sure to include a healthy dose of rotational oblique exercises and even add in weighted exercises to be sure that you‚Äôre building the muscle and training it hard enough to make a difference in its appearance.Here is where you want to be sure that you‚Äôre doing your ab exercises right. The bicycle crunch and russian twists are two moves that many people screw up when trying to train for a trim waistline. Don‚Äôt just flip your hands and elbows across your body but be sure to rotate as you do. Lock your hands or elbows in place and rotate your entire torso as you move to really etch in those deep oblique muscles. Finally, don‚Äôt forget the broom stick twist. This classic oblique exercise is great for giving you high quality contractions of the obliques to make them pop out as you lose the love handle fat laying over the top of them.If you‚Äôre looking for a step by step workout program that includes a meal plan to help you lose fat fast, be sure to head to athleanx.com via the link below and use the program selector to find the workout plan best suited to your goals. Build ripped muscle while training like an athlete in the comfort of your own home.For more videos on how to lose love handles and how to get rid of waistline fat be sure to subscribe to our channel on youtube via the link below and remember to turn on your notifications so you never miss a new video when it‚Äôs published.Build ripped athletic muscle here - http://athleanx.com/x/my-workoutsSubscribe to this channel here - http://bit.ly/2b0coMW

title: The Mandalorian Season 2 Episode 5 Full Breakdown
tags: ahsoka tano|the mandalorian|star wars|the mandalorian season 2 episode 5|the mandalorian season 2|baby yoda|mandalorian season 2|the child|disney plus|mandalorian season 2 episode 5|ahsoka tano the mandalorian|grand admiral thrawn|mandalorian ahsoka|rosario dawson|the mandalorian season 2 episode 5 explained|ahsoka mandalorian|the mandalorian easter eggs|ahsoka leak|thrawn in mandalorian|bo katan|moff gideon|star wars theory|star wars explained
description: WHAT AN AMAZING EPISODE!Things start off insane with Ahsoka Tano played by Rosario Dawson, wielding her white lightsaber blades on Corvus. Dave Filoni directed this and he did an amazing job.As we see the barren forest land of Corvus, we spot a major Easter egg, which is the Owl, Morai. Morai is the daughter. For those who haven‚Äôt watched the clone wars, then you‚Äôll want to watch my video I made on her (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UD_c8JNUSts) which explains everything about her and Mortis.Ahsoka shows up and fights Mando, which ends quick after Mando tells her he was sent by Bo Katan.As she looks at Baby Yoda, our episode really begins.Ahsoka and Baby Yoda talk over the moonlight, where she reveals his name is Grogu. She says they can feel each other‚Äôs thoughts.He was raised at the Jedi temple on coruscant. Many masters trained him over the years. At the end of the clone wars, he was hidden. Someone took him from the temple, then his memory becomes dark.He was lost and alone. So someone has taken his memory. I think there are three people here who could have taken him. One being Mace Windu. Perhaps Mace went directly to the Temple after he fell, and collected Grogu. Or it was Palpatine, who had taken him and that‚Äôs why his memory is dark, because maybe he tried to wipe his mind of things, vital things that had to do with the experiments done on Grogu. Or, Jocastu Nu took him, the librarian. Now, she could have taken him, and when she died months after revenge of the Sith, to Vader, which I‚Äôve covered in a video from the marvel comic, I‚Äôll also link below for you, Grogu was on his own and he had to suppress his powers heavily in order to survive. Like Obi-Wan and Yoda did, so that the empire will not find him.The next day Ahsoka trains Grogu, or at least tries. She failed to get Grogu to summon the stone, where Mando tries to get him to summon the knob of the ship‚Äôs shifter. It works and Grogu takes the knob with the force. Ahsoka realizes they have a strong bond, and says she can‚Äôt train him, for his attachment to Din is too strong. The entire tone of the episode changes when she tells him she‚Äôs seen what attachments do to a fully trained Jedi Knight, she is referring to Anakin Skywalker here, who turned to the dark side due to his attachment to Padme and trying to saver her from dying in child birth, which I would argue, was just a dream put into his head by Palpatine. Din makes a deal with her, that she promises to train the child if he helps her defeat the village who hired him to kill her.Ahsoka and Din Djarin take out the town.Facing the magistrate, she toys with her and disarms her, and demands to know where Grand Admiral Thrawn is.Thrawn is out there.Anyhow, the village is freed, and Mando goes to fetch Grogu to give him up to Ahsoka so he can be trained. Meeting him back at his ship, Ahsoka tells Din that she cannot train Grogu. The attachment he has to Din is far too strong. Mando tells him that a deal is a deal, and she alters the deal, but tells him of another way, she tells him to go to Tython, there he will find the ancient ruins of a temple that is strong in the force, place him atop the mountain on the seeing stone, so that Grogu may choose his path. If he reaches out in the force, a Jedi will sense his presence and come looking for him. In my opinion, this Jedi, is Luke Skywalker. I think what will happen is that Luke, who is getting ready to start building his new temple of Jedi students, will feel Grogu and will reach back out to him, to which the connection will be broken by the interference and arrival of Moff Gideon, who has tracked Mando to Tython and unleashes the dark troopers upon him and Grogu. I believe he‚Äôll then kidnap Grogu to kill him for his blood, where Luke Skywalker will come into the scene somehow to help Din get back the child.I think this will all lead to Luke Skywalker who will train Grogu, but not before Moff Gideon takes him from The Mandalorian!Thrawn top 10 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RD77ZsEwhX4The Daughter - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UD_c8JNUStsBecome a Patron to support future content - https://www.patreon.com/StarWarsTheoryJoin this channel to get access to perks:https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC8CbFnDTYkiVweaz8y9wd_Q/join
